title: 'Looks Sturdy and All in one product for home and professional'
body: It is just overview review not based on actual use. I purchased this for home use, I am not the professional. Reviews are not satisfied for the product yet I chose this because of reasonable price and I don't have heavy use, plus there are tons of useful utility at one place. It is very organised and product looks professional. Overall good purchase and definitely useful for home use. go for it. Only thing noticed on dry run is there is sparking inside the machine. I don't know I should worry about it or not. Let's hope for the best.

title: 'The drill is surprisingly good for the price'
body: Awesome bits and screw accessories in this price range. I have used this drill enough to say it's strong enough to be useful. I am happy with the thin at this for the offered price. The accessories are made of alloys. The screwdriver tips I tried for home carpentry work. I wouldn't try to use the bits or screwdriver tips for anything more than very LIGHT use. It's good to have the bits and tips for when you need them. The drill and the case, however, makes it worth the purchase price.
